  "detailed_description": "In the House of Silence is a roguelike dungeon crawler RPG influenced by classic weird fiction.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Mutate Into Something Inhuman</h2><br>Change your stats by mutating your body parts.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1378870/extras/e5160f3fc94ed097be09b2a1e31b1098.poster.avif?t=1667216210\" width=600 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1378870/extras/e5160f3fc94ed097be09b2a1e31b1098.webm?t=1667216210\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1378870/extras/e5160f3fc94ed097be09b2a1e31b1098.mp4?t=1667216210\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Stave Off Insanity</h2><br>Manage your sanity to prevent alterations to your perception of reality.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1378870/extras/68f67e4ba508de6b706bd14e51f771a6.poster.avif?t=1667216210\" width=374 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1378870/extras/68f67e4ba508de6b706bd14e51f771a6.webm?t=1667216210\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1378870/extras/68f67e4ba508de6b706bd14e51f771a6.mp4?t=1667216210\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Learn the Truth of the House of Silence</h2><br>Explore the ever-changing House of Silence to learn the truth of this new universe you find yourself in.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1378870/extras/4983fc527a956c403e972a0c18ef0079.poster.a